<i>how beautiful it is here.</i>

31
00:04:49,692 --> 00:04:52,228
<i>Ah,</i>
<i>we almost forgot</i>
<i>how beautiful you are, Beth.</i>

32
00:04:52,328 --> 00:04:53,629
<i>-Oh, stop!</i>

33
00:04:53,728 --> 00:04:55,331
Keep going!

34
00:04:55,497 --> 00:04:58,200
Gretchen, come say hi.

35
