Gretchen.

36
00:05:02,737 --> 00:05:05,174
-What's up?
-Oh, Jesus.

37
00:05:05,341 --> 00:05:07,443
<i>Nice to meet you.</i>
<i>Willkommen.</i>

38
00:05:07,543 --> 00:05:08,477
Thank you.

39
00:05:08,577 --> 00:05:09,811
No, thank you, Beth.

40
00:05:09,911 --> 00:05:12,181
