41
00:05:12,481 --> 00:05:15,817
And please do not worry
about your late arrival.

42
00:05:15,917 --> 00:05:17,086
I completely understand.

43
00:05:17,186 --> 00:05:20,222
<i>We have something</i>
<i>for you.</i>

