00:05:26,161 --> 00:05:28,796
We drew that up the night
that you showed us

48
00:05:28,896 --> 00:05:30,599
the land you acquired.

49
00:05:30,733 --> 00:05:32,668
Beth, that is...

50
00:05:33,202 --> 00:05:37,673
Well, we will display
this in the new guest lodge.

51
00:05:37,872 --> 00:05:40,509
- Oh!
<i>- You know, you two lovebirds</i>

52
