77
00:09:58,734 --> 00:10:00,269
Oh, me too.

78
00:10:02,204 --> 00:10:04,039
<i>Are you the housekeeper?</i>

79
00:10:04,273 --> 00:10:05,841
No, I'm a daughter.

80
00:10:06,009 --> 00:10:07,476
Oh, really?

81
00:10:07,776 --> 00:10:09,211
Haven't heard about you.

82
00:10:09,378 --> 00:10:11,647
