85
00:10:15,317 --> 00:10:16,852
I told...

86
00:10:16,953 --> 00:10:18,220
Jesus.

87
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,788
Forgive me, my dear.

88
00:10:21,723 --> 00:10:23,292
Didn't mean to startle you.

89
00:10:23,458 --> 00:10:25,827
