about your family.

90
00:10:25,928 --> 00:10:29,331
Dr. Bonomo is the medical
superintendent
of the local hospital

91
00:10:29,431 --> 00:10:33,235
and also the chronic disease
treatment facility,

92
00:10:33,335 --> 00:10:35,470
which I am also funding.

93
00:10:36,238 --> 00:10:38,340
<i>This is Gretchen.</i>

94
00:10:38,507 --> 00:10:39,675
Gretchen.

95
00:10:40,742 --> 00:10:42,011
Yeah.

96
00:10:42,244 --> 00:10:45,547
Gretchen is from
the United States.

97
00:10:46,381 --> 00:10:49,651
It has been decided
that she is moving in
with her father.

98
00:10:53,255 --> 00:10:54,856
What a pleasant surprise.

99
00:11:02,097 --> 00:11:05,100
<i>Hi,</i>
<i>you have reached</i>
<i>the Vanderkurt residence.</i>

100
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,402
