<i>are here now,</i>

101
00:11:07,502 --> 00:11:09,905
<i>but we are dying to hear</i>
<i>what you have to say,</i>

102
00:11:10,006 --> 00:11:12,341
<i>so get ready to say it.</i>

103
00:11:15,911 --> 00:11:17,245
Hi, mom.

104
00:11:22,085 --> 00:11:24,319
I know this is weird, um...

105
00:11:25,989 --> 00:11:28,156
