Hey, Alma!
What the fuck are you doing?

187
00:18:08,958 --> 00:18:10,960
<i>Gretchen, turn it down!</i>

188
00:18:11,494 --> 00:18:12,560
Alma?

189
00:18:13,728 --> 00:18:16,232
Shh, it's okay, it's okay.

190
00:18:22,038 --> 00:18:24,373
<i>What happened</i>
<i>to your face?</i>

191
00:18:24,906 --> 00:18:29,145
My father's daughter
scratched me.

192
00:18:30,413 --> 00:18:31,546
Your sister?

193
00:18:31,813 --> 00:18:34,016
-She's not my sister.
<i>-Oh.</i>

194
00:18:34,116 --> 00:18:35,351
Come on now.

195
00:18:35,617 --> 00:18:38,653
I'm sure she really wants you
to be her sister.

196
00:18:43,725 --> 00:18:46,761
She had a chance at getting one
but she ate her twin.

197
00:18:51,033 --> 00:18:53,868
<i>It's called vanishing twin</i>
<i>syndrome.</i>

198
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:58,606
It's when one fetus dies
in the early stages
of the pregnancy

199
00:18:58,940 --> 00:19:03,045
and then the surviving fetus
absorbs the dead one.

200
00:19:03,512 --> 00:19:05,814
<i>I always thought</i>
<i>it was kind of badass.</i>

201
00:19:07,715 --> 00:19:09,218
But yeah, she's a bitch.

202
00:19:11,554 --> 00:19:12,754
Okay.

203
00:19:15,924 --> 00:19:18,060
Another reason to not have kids.

204
00:19:19,328 --> 00:19:20,795
<i>Thanks for finishing my shift.</i>

205
00:19:20,895 --> 00:19:23,832
<i>Erik and I haven't been</i>
<i>on a date in ages.</i>

206
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,633
Here's my master key.

207
00:19:26,068 --> 00:19:28,137
There's only one. Don't lose it.

208
00:19:28,404 --> 00:19:32,341
And at 10 p.m. sharp
you lock everything up
like I showed you.

209
00:19:32,774 --> 00:19:34,676
And boss doesn't
need to know.

210
00:19:35,411 --> 00:19:36,312
It's fine.

211
00:19:36,412 --> 00:19:37,246
Okay.

212
00:19:40,513 --> 00:19:42,682
