230
00:21:28,624 --> 00:21:29,959
Sure.

231
00:21:33,728 --> 00:21:36,398
Then you should come to Paris.

232
00:21:42,438 --> 00:21:43,905
Okay.

233
00:22:04,326 --> 00:22:05,327
Hey!

234
00:22:09,365 --> 00:22:11,066
